f̶̑i̸̓̄m̸͌s̸̍͝ḩ̸̎e̴̍̏ 🦖 2023-02-08 7:45 AM
As for paper types and their uses, it all boils down to this: • high gloss and canvas are best for high-quality display • semi-gloss is also good for display, but is more temporary, unless preserved behind glass • matte is more technical, and is meant to be treated as either easily usable and disposable sheets, or interactive documents that may be preserved in laminate
